[I] A GTK+3 SPICE widget

[T] It features glib-based objects for SPICE protocol parsing and a gtk
[T] widget for embedding the SPICE display into other applications such as
[T] virt-manager or Boxes. Python and Vala bindings are available too.

[U] https://www.spice-space.org/download.html

[A] Yaniv Kamay <ykamay@redhat.com> {Original project author}
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

